OL,9,     FSpeeders
OL,10,     GNorthumbria Police face a daily
OL,11,     Gbattle with dangerous and illegal
OL,12,     Gmotorbike use. In Newcastle, cops
OL,13,     Gpursue - by car and chopper - a
OL,14,     Ggroup riding off-road.
